sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid fragments
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid loop, alt, else, and opt fragment transforms.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/06-fragments/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/06-fragments
}
participant Caller
participant Service
loop Retry while pending [Mermaid: loop Retry while pending]
Caller->>Service: Retry request [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Retry request]
end
alt Success branch [Mermaid: alt Success branch]
Caller->>Service: Success path [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Success path]
else Failure branch [Mermaid: else Failure branch]
opt Audit branch [Mermaid: opt Audit branch]
Service->>Caller: Emit audit event [Mermaid: Service->>Caller: Emit audit event]
end
Note over Caller,Service: Failure branch note [Mermaid: Note over Caller,Service: Failure branch note]
Caller->>Service: Failure path [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Failure path]
end
